Activiteit = Activity

Dienst rit = A tour/drive in which the bus transports passengers (in minutes).

Materiaal rit = Any tour/drive in which the bus does not transport passengers (in minutes).

Idle (time) = The amount of time in minutes a bus is not in use.

Opladen = Charging the battery of the bus (in minutes).




KPI's berekeningen
Battery use = All the ... summed up together (in kWh).
Total idle time = All the idle time thingies summed up together (in minutes).

